WEBVTT

00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:03.370
If an Employee is not satisfied with the facility's response

00:00:03.436 --> 00:00:05.572
during the informal classification review,

00:00:05.638 --> 00:00:09.376
he or she can file a classification appeal.

00:00:09.442 --> 00:00:13.346
To begin this appeal, the Employee or the Local can

00:00:13.413 --> 00:00:17.217
request and receive copies of procedures from the Department

00:00:17.283 --> 00:00:20.120
for filing a classification appeal through Department and

00:00:20.186 --> 00:00:22.122
OPM channels.

00:00:22.188 --> 00:00:24.224
The process for filing is next.


